negotiator.timeline

Enum Timeline.Type

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Timeline.Type>
      • negotiator.timeline.Timeline.Type
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Enclosing class:
    Timeline

    public static enum Timeline.Type
extends java.lang.Enum<Timeline.Type>
    In a time-based protocol, time passes within a round. In contrast, in a rounds-based protocol time only passes when the action is presented.
